{"tid":210034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【姚明專用？】雲南當局設意見箱 離地逾2米","createTime":"2017-04-20T16:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T01:29:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72d9167bd1d48f704f36ed59f7023ca660174653","tid":210034,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XiU7QqN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXiU7QqN.png&h=9d872067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雲南省昭通市彝良縣旅遊局，竟然將意見箱掛在2米高的牆上，比一般人高很多，不少民眾都批評這箱要不是給身高2.29米（7尺6寸）的姚明使用，就是根本不想讓人交意見。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民拍下這個意見箱，這與現在熱播電視劇《人民的名義》中「又矮又小」的信訪局窗口如出一轍，有追看的網民稱：「要請達康書記出馬！」<br />\n彝良縣的官員稱，這個意見箱以前的位置較低，可是卻不斷發生路人被撞，於是便請人將位置「調高」。現在的位置是修理後的位置，官員辯稱位置未有驗修便被網民拍到，已經找人再次調整位置。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170420/56590323\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170420%2F56590323&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b08e26dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170420%2F56590323&h=1c1d4567\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170420/56590323</a>"},{"pid":"f7dfe3c8c4eb2b49c453721d392991e25a17d0dd","tid":210034,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T16:07:04.000Z","msg":"唔識擔梯咩<br />\n衣家啲人淨係識反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957766875e1fa4bdd9fe3b3a9cdab3a557a96c1a","tid":210034,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"真係離晒地"},{"pid":"f2cda7052b41fe411931505da31b48ce267499c5","tid":210034,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T17:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d4a9ca713fa0f7f41519cca9d69cde06d7d961","tid":210034,"